21:42.001 --> 21:44.336 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DOMENICO MONTANARO, Political
Editor, NPR:
Well, first of all, going into
Election Day,

21:44.370 --> 21:47.306 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
