wall, we're talking about that
Upper Midwest.

23:27.072 --> 23:29.508 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And we see that in light blue
color.

23:29.541 --> 23:32.811 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Domenico, I want to turn you now
to talk about
exit polls.

23:32.845 --> 23:36.081 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
