runs them?

23:38.651 --> 23:44.657 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DOMENICO MONTANARO: So, exit
polls are commissioned
by the national media, the big
broadcast organizations,

23:44.690 --> 23:49.995 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
