The New York
Times, The Washington Post, ABC,
NBC, CNN,

23:50.029 --> 23:51.830 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for example.

23:51.864 --> 23:55.768 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
