Research, which
does -- creates what's called
the National

23:55.801 --> 23:57.970 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Exit Poll Consortium.

23:58.003 --> 23:59.772 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
