should say, PBS,
NPR, we're not participating in
it this time

24:04.476 --> 24:05.944 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
around.

24:05.978 --> 24:07.780 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So when you see those numbers,
they will be
coming from that consortium.

24:07.813 --> 24:11.517 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And they -- what
