interview people
after they have left the polls.

24:15.154 --> 24:16.355 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DOMENICO MONTANARO: That's
right.

24:16.388 --> 24:19.124 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
