people as part
of the sample.

24:19.158 --> 24:24.463 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And why that's really amazing is
that, when
you think about a normal
national poll, there's

24:24.496 --> 24:27.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
