get them to
take a questionnaire, fill it
out and then

24:44.516 --> 24:46.218 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that information is relayed
back.

24:46.251 --> 24:49.421 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, Domenico, we
have heard
so much this year about how big
the early

