40-some million
people voting early.

24:54.226 --> 24:57.029 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
How do they measure those votes,
or absentee
votes, for example?

24:57.062 --> 25:01.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DOMENICO MONTANARO: Well, when
it comes to
exit polling early voters, they
will do a

25:01.433 --> 25:03.168 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
phone, a normal phone poll.

25:03.202 --> 25:07.106 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So they will call a place like
Washington
state or Oregon or Colorado,
where they do

25:07.139 --> 25:13.112 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
