that they can
get demographic information to
plug into the

25:13.145 --> 25:15.147 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
exit poll.

25:15.180 --> 25:17.516 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And then so those
news organizations
that are part of this, they're
the ones, including

25:17.549 --> 25:22.287 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
