headed, then
they can make a call.

25:47.679 --> 25:49.381 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Now, I should say one thing.

25:49.415 --> 25:52.785 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When you see a lot of the places
that call
a state with zero percent in or
1 percent

25:52.818 --> 25:58.157 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in, it's very rarely that state
that gets
it wrong, because, historically,
that's usually

25:58.190 --> 26:00.526 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
