where we will be waiting and
waiting and maybe

26:16.608 --> 26:17.910 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
waiting.

26:17.943 --> 26:19.678 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DOMENICO MONTANARO: Right, in
those states
too close to call.

26:19.711 --> 26:21.847 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And if they are too close to
call, you're
looking at later in the night,
11:00 at the

26:21.880 --> 26:25.484 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
