that's when
it's been called in the last two
elections.

26:25.517 --> 26:26.752 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We can't wait.

26:26.785 --> 26:27.920 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We're all on the edge of our
seats.

26:27.953 --> 26:29.188 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DOMENICO MONTANARO: It's almost
over.

26:29.221 --> 26:30.456 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
