greatness that
they were seeing.

50:08.939 --> 50:09.907 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
But I digress.

50:09.940 --> 50:11.408 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I wish you both the best.

50:11.442 --> 50:14.912 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If we give you the keys to our
world, you
got to promise us true freedom.

50:14.945 --> 50:18.249 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Truly yours, the black nation,
the people
you should be healing.

